---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import MediaText from '../components/MediaText.astro';
import FullBleed from '../components/FullBleed.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import artsPhoto from '../assets/images/artandcraftpupils.jpg';
import curiosityPhoto from '../assets/images/sciencepupils.jpg';
import communityPhoto from '../assets/images/culturalattireday.jpg';
import welcomePhoto from '../assets/images/outdoorplay.jpg';
---
<Layout
  title="School Life — Mt Cedar British International School"
  description="Beyond the classroom at Mt Cedar British International School: sport and the arts, character and community, pastoral care and a safe, joyful place to grow."
  active="school-life"
>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">School Life</p>
    <h1>Learning that reaches beyond the classroom.</h1>
    <p>At Mt Cedar, character is built in the everyday — in friendships, sport, the arts, service and the small habits of a well-lived school day.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head"><p class="eyebrow">A Full School Day</p><h2>Room to explore, belong and shine.</h2><p>We want children to leave each day a little more confident, a little more curious, and glad to come back tomorrow.</p></div>
    <div class="feat-grid">
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 3a15 15 0 0 0 0 18M12 3a15 15 0 0 1 0 18M3 12h18"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Sport &amp; Play</h3>
        <p>Active, healthy days with games and physical education that build teamwork, resilience and joy in movement.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M12 3v10.55A4 4 0 1 0 14 17V7h4V3Z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Arts &amp; Music</h3>
        <p>Creative expression through music, drama and the visual arts — space for every child to discover a talent.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M12 21s-7-4.5-7-10a4 4 0 0 1 7-2.6A4 4 0 0 1 19 11c0 5.5-7 10-7 10Z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Character &amp; Service</h3>
        <p>Honesty, kindness and courage, practised through everyday responsibility and care for one another.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M12 2 3 7v6c0 5 3.5 8 9 9 5.5-1 9-4 9-9V7l-9-5Z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Safe &amp; Nurturing</h3>
        <p>A secure, welcoming environment where pastoral care means every child is known, supported and valued.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><circle cx="9" cy="8" r="3"/><path d="M3 20a6 6 0 0 1 12 0"/><path d="M16 6a3 3 0 0 1 0 6"/><path d="M18 20a6 6 0 0 0-3-5.2"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Community</h3>
        <p>A close partnership between pupils, parents and staff — celebrated together on Founder’s Day and beyond.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="26" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M2 12s3-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3 7-10 7-10-7-10-7Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Curiosity &amp; Enquiry</h3>
        <p>Clubs, projects and real-world learning — like our science fair — that turn wondering into discovery.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<MediaText
  image={artsPhoto}
  alt="Mt Cedar pupils enjoying art and craft"
  eyebrow="Creativity"
  title="Arts, music and making."
  background="var(--ivory-2)"
>
  <p>From art and craft to music and drama, we give every child room to create, perform and discover a talent. Creative work builds confidence, focus and joy — and it belongs at the heart of a good education.</p>
</MediaText>

<FullBleed
  image={communityPhoto}
  alt="Mt Cedar pupils in cultural attire celebrating together"
  eyebrow="Our Community"
  title="A school that celebrates together."
>
  <p>Founder’s Day, cultural showcases and everyday moments of togetherness — Mt Cedar is a warm community where pupils, parents and staff belong.</p>
</FullBleed>

<MediaText
  image={curiosityPhoto}
  alt="Young Mt Cedar scientists exploring a project"
  eyebrow="Curiosity in Action"
  title="Where wondering becomes discovery."
  reverse={true}
>
  <p>Clubs, hands-on projects and events like our science fair turn everyday curiosity into real learning. We want children to ask questions, test ideas, and delight in finding things out for themselves.</p>
</MediaText>

<section class="welcome">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="photo">
      <Image src={welcomePhoto} alt="Mt Cedar children at outdoor play" widths={[480, 768, 1100]} sizes="(max-width: 820px) 92vw, 46vw" format="webp" quality={74} loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Our Community</p>
      <h2>Every child known by name.</h2>
      <blockquote>“Character isn’t taught in a single lesson — it’s grown in a thousand small moments across a school day. That is the work we love most.”</blockquote>
      <div class="signoff">The Mt Cedar Team<small>Excellence · Character · Growth</small></div>
      <div class="cta" style="margin-top:1.6rem">
        <a class="btn btn-cedar" href="/contact">Come and Visit <span class="arr">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="band">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--gold-bright)">See it for yourself</p>
    <h2>The best way to know Mt Cedar is to visit.</h2>
    <p>Spend a morning with us and see what a Mt Cedar school day feels like for your child.</p>
    <div class="cta">
      <a class="btn btn-gold btn-lg" href="/contact">Arrange a Visit <span class="arr">→</span></a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg" href="/admissions">See Admissions</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
